<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
  <head>
    <title>NUTV - Home</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="NUTV Website">
    <meta name="keywords" content="NUTV, Northeastern, University, Television">
    <meta name="author" content="Eric Gift">
  </head>
  <body class="homebody">
    <div class="header">
      <a id="logo" href="/home"><img src="/assets/nutv.jpg"/></a>
      <% if current_user %>
      <a href="/news/projects">News</a>
      <a href="/sports/projects">Sports</a>
      <a href="/entertainment/projects">Entertainment</a>
      <a href="/projects">All</a>
      <% else %>
      <a href="/news">News</a>
      <a href="/sports">Sports</a>
      <a href="/entertainment">Entertainment</a>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="homeimage">
        <img id="camera" src="/assets/camera.png" alt="camera" />
       <div class="rightlink">
        <h2>
          Connect with us!
        </h2>
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/northeasterntv#"> <img class="circles" src="/assets/facebookcircle.png" alt="fb" /> </a>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/NUTV"> <img class="circles" src="/assets/twittercircle.png" alt="twitter" /> </a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/northeasternuniversitytv/"> <img class="circles" src="/assets/instagramcircle.png" alt="insta" /></a>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCvc7BC4Q8qEu-2YUUu4BI7Q"> <img class="circles" src="/assets/youtubecircle.png" alt="yt" /></a>
      </div>
     <div class="rightbox">
      <div class="accountbox">
        <% if current_user %>
        <h2>
          Hello, <%= current_user.first_name %>!
        </h2>
          <%= link_to user_path(current_user) do %>
            <div id="loginbox" class="profile">
              <p>
                Account
              </p>
            <img class="go" src="/assets/go.png" alt="go" />
          </div>
         <% end %>
        <%= link_to logout_path, method: "delete" do %>
          <div id="signupbox" class="profile">
            <p>
              Logout
            </p>
            <img class="go" src="/assets/go.png" alt="go" />
        </div>
        </div>
           <% end %>
        <div class="socialbox">
        <a href="/entertainment/projects">
          <div id="fbbox" class="sbox">
            <p>
              entertainment
            </p>
            <img class="masks" src="/assets/masks.png"/>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/sports/projects">
          <div id="twitterbox" class="sbox">
            <p>
             sports
            </p>
            <img class="basketball" src="/assets/basketball.png"/>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/news/projects">
          <div id="instabox" class="sbox">
            <p>
              news
            </p>
            <img class="mic" src="/assets/mic.png"/>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
        <% else %>
          <h2>
            Welcome to NUTV!
          </h2>
          <a class="aprofile" href="/login">
            <div id="loginbox" class="profile" >
              <p>
                Login
              </p>
              <img class="go" src="/assets/go.png" alt="go" />
            </div>
            </a>
        <a class="aprofile" href="/signup">
          <div id="signupbox" class="profile">
            <p>
              Signup
            </p>
            <img class="go" src="/assets/go.png" alt="go" />
          </div>
           </a>
        <div class="promodiv">
           <iframe class="promovid" width="700" height="420" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/PnkZjQa1-d4" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>

       <% end %>
       </div>
      </div>

    <div class="content">
       <div class="aboutus">
        <h3>
          About Us
        </h3>
        <p>
          NUTV (Northeastern Television) is a video production club on campus, offering those with or without

production experience an opportunity to make videos (and also friends!). Equipped with a drone, a

steady cam, editing software, and numerous tripods, DSLRs, lenses, mics, and FX cameras, NUTV

members have the freedom to work with different equipment and produce videos of different styles

and genres. Specifically, each of NUTVâ€™s three departments (News, Sports, and Entertainment) also

specialize in different facets of video production, so feel free to explore what each department does.

Ultimately, NUTV is a teaching and learning club in addition to a production club, and we love helping

people make awesome productions. Everyone is welcome, so come by, learn, make, and have a good

time!
        </p>
      </div>
      <img class="videocamera" src="/assets/videocamera.png" alt="videocamera" />
      <div class="nav">
        <a class="eboard" id="eboardlink" href="/eboard"><div>
          E-Board
          <img class="gob" src="/assets/go.png" alt="go" />
        </div></a>
        <a class="eboard" id="contactlink" href="/contact"><div>
          Contact
          <img class="gob" src="/assets/go.png" alt="go" />
        </div></a>
      </div>
        <div class="videos">
          <h2>
            The Latest From NUTV
          </h2>
          <div class="videocontainer">
            <iframe class="grid" src="https://www.youtube.com/v/videoseries?list=PL3s6etJXhUBH9xuGzqSRiT4sCq6Hy6SFc&index=0"></iframe>
          </div>
          <div class="videocontainer">
            <iframe class="grid" src="https://www.youtube.com/v/videoseries?list=PL3s6etJXhUBH9xuGzqSRiT4sCq6Hy6SFc&index=1"></iframe>
          </div>
          <div class="videocontainer">
            <iframe class="grid" src="https://www.youtube.com/v/videoseries?list=PL3s6etJXhUBH9xuGzqSRiT4sCq6Hy6SFc&index=2"></iframe>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <h3>
        Design by <a href="http://www.ericjgift.com">Eric Gift</a>, 2016
      </h3>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
